    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-02-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-02-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="841"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d841">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">822.61334/68</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Ecuador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hartman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-02-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 9, 1922</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received March 2.]</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 787</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to the Department’s instruction No.
                    296, of December 5, 1921, relative to the understanding reached between the
                    President of Ecuador and the representative of the Mercantile Bank of the
                    Americas regarding the payment to the latter of the debt of the Association of
                    Agriculturists, I have the honor to transmit herewith copy and translation of an
                    informal communication from the President, dated February 5, 1922,<note n="45"
                        xml:id="d841fn45">Not printed.</note> in which he confirms the terms of the
                    agreement.</p>
                <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Chas. S. Hartman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
